Class OrderTrendsController.Order

java.lang.Object
com.example.controllers.OrderTrendsController.Order
Enclosing class:
OrderTrendsController
public static class OrderTrendsController.Order extends Object
Data Transfer Object representing an order with essential information. This class encapsulates order data retrieved from the database for display and analysis purposes.
